        "TileImage": "$($repository 1595c70e-1f16-44c1-878a-21a93cd9fb12).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening, 47. Today, you&apos;ll return to Sapienza, Italy, in order to dismantle the political advisory staff of one Marco Abiatti. A right-wing populist with criminal connections, a love of fossil fuels, and remarkable ambition to entrench himself in power, he&apos;s recently made the list of potential candidates for Providence. Eliminate his campaign manager, Roberto Mulo, head of security - and intimidation - Matteo Davide, and top donor, Donato Tromba, and his chances of winning decline sharply.",
